    <item>
      <title>特朗普目标是在最新的大门举动中进行工会谈判的支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-targets-spending-on-labor-union-talks-in-latest-doge-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的政府要求联邦机构报告他们在过去一年中花费了多少谈判工会合同，这表明集体谈判协议可能是政府削减成本推动力的下一个目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-targets-spending-on-labor-union-talks-in-latest-doge-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 22:33:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国和欧盟提前谈论抓住冻结的俄罗斯资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/uk-and-eu-advance-talks-on-seizing-frozen-russian-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国和欧洲联盟将就如何抓住冻结的俄罗斯资产来共同提高国防支出的方式进行谈判，因为他们寻求在任何和平谈判之前对弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）提高经济压力的方法，以结束他对乌克兰的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/uk-and-eu-advance-talks-on-seizing-frozen-russian-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普利用共和国航空首席执行官领导美国航空监管机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-taps-republic-airways-ceo-to-lead-us-aviation-regulator</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）提名了区域航空公司Airways Holdings Inc.首席执行官布莱恩·贝德福德（Bryan Bedford），成为联邦航空管理局的下一任领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-taps-republic-airways-ceo-to-lead-us-aviation-regulator</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 22:01:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼说，加拿大有限匹配美国的关税。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/canada-is-limited-in-matching-further-us-tariffs-carney-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）说，加拿大只有在应对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对经济体之间的不匹配的新关税时才能做出如此远。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/canada-is-limited-in-matching-further-us-tariffs-carney-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 21:29:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国顶级法院拒绝更多试图停止债务刹车投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/german-top-court-rejects-more-attempts-to-stop-debt-brake-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国最高法院驳回了额外的企图，以防止国家即将离任的议会对宪法进行更改，以消除国防借贷的限制，并建立了5000亿欧元（5460亿美元）的基础设施基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/german-top-court-rejects-more-attempts-to-stop-debt-brake-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 20:59:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说他从不喜欢肯尼迪中心的“汉密尔顿”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-says-he-never-liked-hamilton-in-visit-to-kennedy-center</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统将肯尼​​迪中心（Kennedy Center）施放，这是美国首要的文化机构之一，处于失修状态，誓言要对标志性场地的结构和编程进行彻底改变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-says-he-never-liked-hamilton-in-visit-to-kennedy-center</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 19:57:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保守派承诺杀死加拿大的工业碳税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/conservatives-promise-to-kill-canada-s-industrial-carbon-tax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大的保守派领导人承诺，如果当选，则保证该国的工业碳价格取消，但对企业的影响程度将取决于省份是否效仿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/conservatives-promise-to-kill-canada-s-industrial-carbon-tax</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 15:55:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对新鲜的胡塞威胁加大对伊朗的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-ramps-up-pressure-on-iran-with-fresh-houthi-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统对伊朗的压力施加了压力，要求他们遏制霍蒂斯（Houthis），如果也门的武装组织没有阻止其袭击，就提高了对伊斯兰共和国进行报复罢工的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-ramps-up-pressure-on-iran-with-fresh-houthi-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 15:43:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
