      <title>秘鲁宣布利马在杀害歌手的紧急状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/peru-to-declare-state-of-emergency-in-lima-after-singer-s-murder</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁当局在周一在一名歌手被谋杀再次引起了勒索球拍的警报后，周一宣布了该国首都30天的紧急状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/peru-to-declare-state-of-emergency-in-lima-after-singer-s-murder</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 14:55:52 GMT</pubDate>
